article.headline: Roberts scores 23, Penn downs Maine 77-64
article.description: — Ethan Roberts had 23 points in Pennsylvania's 77-64 win against Maine on Saturday night.
article.story: PHILADELPHIA -- — Ethan Roberts had 23 points in Pennsylvania's 77-64 win against Maine on Saturday night. Roberts added 10 rebounds and three steals for the Quakers (3-4). Sam Brown scored 19 points, going 3 of 8 from the floor and 13 for 14 from the line. Nick Spinoso went 6 of 12 from the field to finish with 14 points, while adding nine rebounds and eight assists. The Black Bears (4-4) were led by Kellen Tynes, who posted 15 points, six assists and three steals. Maine also got 13 points from Quion Burns. AJ Lopez had 13 points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
